description.narrative: The extensive process participated by multi-stakeholders for child protection system mapping, visioning and planning resulted in the availability of an assessment report, a child protection system vision framework and plan of actions with social welfare workforce development strategy. Robust advocacy on the CRC Concluding Observations resulted in a Government Notification on the implementation of the recommendations for CRC/CEDAW. UNICEF also supported in drafting the concept paper “Strengthening Social Protection for Vulnerable Children in ASEAN” with a linkage to the child protection system for the 14th ASEAN GO-NGO Forum on Social Welfare and Development hosted by the Lao Government. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
